overview: Straight from the twisted mind of director (and Girlfriends founder) Dan O'Connell, Messed Up! Episode 6 features returning cast members Chanel Preston and Violet Starr, along with Vanessa Veracruz reprising her role as the dashingly handsome, and now ordained, Valentino. In a Girlfriends Films press release earlier this year, director O'Connell referred to the Vanessa/Valentino transformation as “eerily extraordinary.”
tagline: Tainted passion turns to obsessed lust!
title: Lesbian PsychoDramas 26
